text: Is it possible to pass data to HubSpot via segment integration if you don't have HubSpot marketing enterprise (ie no customer events)

*Has anyone else experienced this?* Error “cannot read property ‘rowsApi’ of undefined” when using the `HubSpotClient.cms.hubdb.rows.rowsApi.getTableRows(tableIdOrName, sort, after, limit, properties);`  from the <https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/api/cms/hubdb|documentation>
